Marcia Ralston https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marcia_Ralston 0 Marcia Mascotte Ralston (19 September 1906 – 23 November 1988) was an Australian born actress who appeared in Hollywood films in the 1930s and 1940s. She was married to Phil Harris between 1927 and 1940.
